OL,3,CSlip and slide attractions slashed by
OL,4,Cvandals - leaving one closed
OL,6,FTwo slip and slide tourist attractions
OL,7,Fin Cornwall have been left thousands
OL,8,Fof pounds out of pocket after being
OL,9,Ftargeted by vandals.
OL,11,FIt is believed the slides have been
OL,12,Fslashed with a knife or other sharp
OL,13,Fobject.
OL,15,FThe first attack happened at Mega Slip
OL,16,Fand Slide, in Blackwater, near Truro,
OL,17,Fovernight on Thursday 15 August.
