OL,3,CSlip and slide attractions slashed by
OL,4,Cvandals - leaving one closed
OL,6,FIt was followed by a second attack at
OL,7,FAvalanche Slip n Slide in East Crinnis
OL,8,FHoliday Park, near St Austell, on
OL,9,FMonday 26 August. Four of its slides
OL,10,Fwere badly damaged.
OL,12,FDevon and Cornwall Police said it has
OL,13,Freceived reports of criminal damage at
OL,14,Fthe attractions and is appealing for
OL,15,Fanyone with information to come
OL,16,Fforward.
OL,18,FDominic McCalwane, owner of Mega Slip
OL,19,Fand Slide, said he was "very
OL,20,Fdisappointed" after discovering one of
OL,21,Fthe slides had been vandalised.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
