OL,6,F"Our customers, they come here for the
OL,7,Fsmiles and for a good time," he said.
OL,9,F"It's disappointing for myself as a
OL,10,Fbusiness owner, but also for the
OL,11,Fcommunity because we bring a lot of
OL,12,Fpeople through this little village."
OL,14,FMr McCalwane said he has spent around
OL,15,F#10,000 repairing the slip and slide
OL,16,Fand installing security cameras at the
OL,17,Fsite in order to be able to continue
OL,18,Ftrading.
