OL,6,F"We've now got 4K imagery of the whole
OL,7,Fsite," he said. "We don't expect to
OL,8,Factually have to do that."
OL,10,FHe added: "It's strange to see a CCTV
OL,11,Fcamera but you have to adapt and
OL,12,Fovercome."
OL,14,FDan Olford, owner of East Crinnis
OL,15,FHoliday Park, said he has been forced
OL,16,Fto close Avalanche Slip n Slide for
OL,17,Fthe foreseeable future due to the
OL,18,Fscale of the damage.
