OL,6,F"We've been through the emotional
OL,7,Frollercoaster of feeling very hurt,
OL,8,Fsad, and upset, trying to understand
OL,9,Fwhy someone would do something like
OL,10,Fthis," he said.
OL,12,FMr Olford said it will cost thousands
OL,13,Fof pounds to repair the slides, which
OL,14,Fare currently not fit for purpose.
OL,16,FDevon and Cornwall Police said it is
OL,17,Fno longer investigating reports of
OL,18,Fcriminal damage at Mega Slip and Slide
OL,19,Fin Truro.
