OL,6,F"At this time, there are no viable
OL,7,Flines of enquiry however if further
OL,8,Fevidence comes to light the incident
OL,9,Fcan be re-visited," a police
OL,10,Fspokesperson said.
OL,12,FThe force said it is investigating
OL,13,Freports of criminal at East Crinnis
OL,14,FHoliday Park and is appealing for
OL,15,Fanyone with information to get in
OL,16,Ftouch.
OL,18,FAnybody with information should call
OL,19,Fpolice on 101 or report via our
OL,20,Fwebsite quoting crime reference
OL,21,F50240216335.
